'''浮动螺母'''也称'''卡式螺母'''，是一种自带调节功能的[[螺母|螺母]]，可补偿配合孔的安装误差。在1950年代初申请专利，最初设计需要用工具将其压入孔内<ref>Laurence H. Flora, Jr., ''Combined Nut Retainer and Thread Lock'', {{US patent|2587134}}, granted Feb. 26, 1952.</ref><ref>William A. Bedford, Jr., ''Cage Nut'', {{US patent|2627294}}, granted Feb. 3, 1953.</ref>。改良后，不需借助工具即可完成安装<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cablinginstall.com/articles/2016/08/chatsworth-products-clik-nut-cage-nuts.html|title=CPI’s Clik-Nut is a tool-less alternative to traditional cage nuts|website=www.cablinginstall.com|access-date=2018-04-25|archive-date=2018-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623085108/https://www.cablinginstall.com/articles/2016/08/chatsworth-products-clik-nut-cage-nuts.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

